          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The angular distribution of  neutrons  from  deuteron",
                " photodisintegration  by  2.75  MeV  gamma  rays  was",
                " measured at six laboratory angles between 30 and 135",
                " degrees. The dipole cross section ratio sig-m/ sig-e",
                " = 0.290 (0.021) was derieved from the  measurements.",
                " The  least  squares  fit  to angular distribution of",
                " neutrons led to the value a/b = 0.193 (0.014)."
              ]
            }
          ],
